{"tid":421142,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"求教 澳洲Cairns大堡礁五日四夜","createTime":"2017-10-02T03:57:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T03:29:05.000Z","uid":90716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6bac5c43945c09f22aebac88c18cd9d4259e8637","tid":421142,"uid":90716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T03:57:57.000Z","msg":"請問有無師兄姐去過cairns?<br />\n<br />\n我想搵一至兩日係出海 想問下綠島同翡翠島有乜野唔同？<br />\n<br />\n熱帶雨林公園同天空之城係咪值得去？<br />\n<br />\n我地係四個人去 有一個唔識游水 會唔會悶親佢？"},{"pid":"aca84ad4b957c453493032470d0edfd60a17ea61","tid":421142,"uid":130474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T04:04:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請問有無師兄姐去過cairns?<br />\n<br />\n我想搵一至兩日係出海 想問下綠島同翡翠島有乜野唔同？<br />\n<br />\n熱帶雨林公園同天空之城係咪值得去？<br />\n<br />\n我地係四個人去 有一個唔識游水 會唔會悶親佢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔識游水可以用救生衣玩浮潛, 都OK...<br />\n只去過綠島, 天氣一般, 就反而唔太好玩.....<br />\n<br />\n後生的話, 我覺得cairns最好玩係激流....玩成日架.....<br />\n<br />\nSOR, 我去講緊成10年前, 唔知有無唔同左......."},{"pid":"bf43aef67bcf99fef1bd3a4b12d89b925f414276","tid":421142,"uid":90716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T04:04:28.000Z","msg":"同埋有無local tour介紹？<br />\n最好就講中文啦 因為同父母去"},{"pid":"5afe24c104f5dd5d0efb9a3f248c703c00d46564","tid":421142,"uid":10157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T04:14:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>請問有無師兄姐去過cairns?<br />\n<br />\n我想搵一至兩日係出海 想問下綠島同翡翠島有乜野唔同？<br />\n<br />\n熱帶雨林公園同天空之城係咪值得去？<br />\n<br />\n我地係四個人去 有一個唔識游水 會唔會悶親佢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔識游水可以用救生衣玩浮潛, 都OK...<br />\n只去過綠島, 天氣一般, 就反而唔太好玩.....<br />\n<br />\n後生的話, 我覺得cairns最好玩係激流....玩成日架.....<br />\n<br />\nSOR, 我去講緊成10年前, 唔知有無唔同左.......</blockquote><br />\n宜家都一樣<br />\n激流條河好長可以由朝流到晚真係好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nCairns唔識游水都可以玩晒全部野<br />\n帶晒救生衣又有人睇住<br />\n深潛都有人拖住<br />\n<br />\n島就熟啦，唔同地方有唔同野睇<br />\n見人地有海龜摸<br />\n上次去join 日團睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n熱帶雨林ok好行，但見唔到d生物<br />\n可以搭下超長纜車<br />\n天空之城聽人講超廢所以無去"},{"pid":"25e4d00dbd59075296987d4aea5bee62f0e9a349","tid":421142,"uid":10157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T04:19:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋有無local tour介紹？<br />\n最好就講中文啦 因為同父母去</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/02/121721_10081aaf58b768228c268fe0cc49c6f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F02%2F121721_10081aaf58b768228c268fe0cc49c6f1.jpg&h=7b6bf30c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幾年前，唔知有冇加價<br />\n研究過平過自由行"},{"pid":"46570d884e061f0252aca837596d03feb3a3b07e","tid":421142,"uid":90716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T05:03:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>請問有無師兄姐去過cairns?<br />\n<br />\n我想搵一至兩日係出海 想問下綠島同翡翠島有乜野唔同？<br />\n<br />\n熱帶雨林公園同天空之城係咪值得去？<br />\n<br />\n我地係四個人去 有一個唔識游水 會唔會悶親佢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔識游水可以用救生衣玩浮潛, 都OK...<br />\n只去過綠島, 天氣一般, 就反而唔太好玩.....<br />\n<br />\n後生的話, 我覺得cairns最好玩係激流....玩成日架.....<br />\n<br />\nSOR, 我去講緊成10年前, 唔知有無唔同左.......</blockquote><br />\n宜家都一樣<br />\n激流條河好長可以由朝流到晚真係好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nCairns唔識游水都可以玩晒全部野<br />\n帶晒救生衣又有人睇住<br />\n深潛都有人拖住<br />\n<br />\n島就熟啦，唔同地方有唔同野睇<br />\n見人地有海龜摸<br />\n上次去join 日團睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n熱帶雨林ok好行，但見唔到d生物<br />\n可以搭下超長纜車<br />\n天空之城聽人講超廢所以無去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見到有個激流係五個鐘好似有啲長 驚坐到暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />應該只會join兩個鐘個個 <br />\n想問下激流會唔會太剌激同安唔安全？"},{"pid":"3c84cce7d67b608631c964469531612638d258c0","tid":421142,"uid":90716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T05:04:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同埋有無local tour介紹？<br />\n最好就講中文啦 因為同父母去</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/02/121721_10081aaf58b768228c268fe0cc49c6f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F02%2F121721_10081aaf58b768228c268fe0cc49c6f1.jpg&h=7b6bf30c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幾年前，唔知有冇加價<br />\n研究過平過自由行</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該晒 我宜家上網睇下"},{"pid":"e5513dffa9e6953e6d0d808379fbce36b18f2fa3","tid":421142,"uid":71824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T05:17:59.000Z","msg":"cairns週圍都旅行社<br />\n<br />\n激流有d低level可以揀"},{"pid":"66b9e944f0abac029e1da441886a705b53420ea9","tid":421142,"uid":90716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T05:47:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>cairns週圍都旅行社<br />\n<br />\n激流有d低level可以揀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n姐係去到cairns先報？"},{"pid":"393310a9b1d632fa79154526eecb4c9b72047c0a","tid":421142,"uid":11388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T12:19:32.000Z","msg":"fittravel幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上年去都book過"},{"pid":"cc1e69ba30e1649c9661343450a9a6d45f61bc33","tid":421142,"uid":145446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T13:07:36.000Z","msg":"有去翡翠島，但有啲失望因為海水好濁，近陸地嘅珊瑚又白化哂，我唔識游水又唔敢出得太遠，所以可以話係乜都睇唔到....聽同團啲人講要游到好出先睇到，如果係為咗浮建議直接報啲出外海嘅團好啲"},{"pid":"461de0f8080b0c94593ff7ac7f51c8b9dd65093d","tid":421142,"uid":90716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T13:57:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有去翡翠島，但有啲失望因為海水好濁，近陸地嘅珊瑚又白化哂，我唔識游水又唔敢出得太遠，所以可以話係乜都睇唔到....聽同團啲人講要游到好出先睇到，如果係為咗浮建議直接報啲出外海嘅團好啲</blockquote><br />\n翡翠島唔係姐係出海團咩？"},{"pid":"1651325025c1e994df2b6b54466aaba9649bdc69","tid":421142,"uid":35365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T16:43:46.000Z","msg":"雨林火車個tour幾抵玩幾多野睇<br />\n兩年前帶兩老去都book fit travel<br />\n服務幾好"},{"pid":"6491f6bc742e51f8f1dea6eb68317d12d957b0d5","tid":421142,"uid":128271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T17:10:49.000Z","msg":"Cairns 除左airbnb 有咩地方可以揀 兩個女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b15aefe9afc3653c0d5a3b824159e5fa0d5b473","tid":421142,"uid":90716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T05:44:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Cairns 除左airbnb 有咩地方可以揀 兩個女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://我用hotel.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%88%91%E7%94%A8hotel.com&d=H5S4o0Ff8XTpADkL962R5o9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=392de8cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">我用hotel.com</a>睇 都好多酒店呀"},{"pid":"8631fcaf04841aa6a38c56308229ecf19a0e24e5","tid":421142,"uid":71824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T15:50:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Cairns 除左airbnb 有咩地方可以揀 兩個女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nhostel?<br />\n2人房"},{"pid":"e6bc7331f2baf6f07af286dafd24cf7846961979","tid":421142,"uid":71824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T15:52:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>cairns週圍都旅行社<br />\n<br />\n激流有d低level可以揀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n姐係去到cairns先報？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一定要玩果d可以book左先<br />\n<br />\n決定唔到果d去到先揀lor"},{"pid":"7380c6b5aeef07261508f2688b3acea88a11bf20","tid":421142,"uid":124735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T16:04:54.000Z","msg":"唔使擔心Day tour好多都有普通話團<br />\n朋友喺綠島見到龜<br />\n好似有啲朋友係另一個島到見到鯊魚添<br />\n上次去俾人sales去大堡礁遠啲嘅島，得啲魚仔咋<br />\n好睇你個潛水既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"288041c7806e850d1404c8021e434d585695e7c2","tid":421142,"uid":128271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T17:46:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Cairns 除左airbnb 有咩地方可以揀 兩個女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我用<a href=\"http://hotel.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhotel.com&d=H5S4o0Ff8XTpADkL962R5o9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=d0a1579e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hotel.com</a>睇 都好多酒店呀</blockquote><br />\n好貴 機票已經好貴"},{"pid":"263e1aae2c056bc37bda156f20c8392e50bd3e4d","tid":421142,"uid":145446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T12:30:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有去翡翠島，但有啲失望因為海水好濁，近陸地嘅珊瑚又白化哂，我唔識游水又唔敢出得太遠，所以可以話係乜都睇唔到....聽同團啲人講要游到好出先睇到，如果係為咗浮建議直接報啲出外海嘅團好啲</blockquote><br />\n翡翠島唔係姐係出海團咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我join嗰個團無帶我哋出海中心度潛水...<br />\n淨係送咗我哋去翡翠島，係海灘間舖仔租器材係個島附近自己游出去玩浮潛"},{"pid":"728174d5e350f106b9fb8c1ec374dcbd3dcd5ad5","tid":421142,"uid":90716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T13:26:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Cairns 除左airbnb 有咩地方可以揀 兩個女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我用<a href=\"http://hotel.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhotel.com&d=H5S4o0Ff8XTpADkL962R5o9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=d0a1579e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hotel.com</a>睇 都好多酒店呀</blockquote><br />\n好貴 機票已經好貴</blockquote><br />\n其實兩個女仔住hostel無問題<br />\n好多人一個女仔都住hostel 記住淨係揀female dorm就安全啲"},{"pid":"e7f72ec961b18d8dbdd13d63750b73a7115e267f","tid":421142,"uid":90716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T13:27:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有去翡翠島，但有啲失望因為海水好濁，近陸地嘅珊瑚又白化哂，我唔識游水又唔敢出得太遠，所以可以話係乜都睇唔到....聽同團啲人講要游到好出先睇到，如果係為咗浮建議直接報啲出外海嘅團好啲</blockquote><br />\n翡翠島唔係姐係出海團咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我join嗰個團無帶我哋出海中心度潛水...<br />\n淨係送咗我哋去翡翠島，係海灘間舖仔租器材係個島附近自己游出去玩浮潛</blockquote><br />\n師兄記唔記得你join邊間同幾錢？"},{"pid":"3d0ef76b7527f3cb4925fd56bd23f8a49314f61d","tid":421142,"uid":145446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T07:16:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有去翡翠島，但有啲失望因為海水好濁，近陸地嘅珊瑚又白化哂，我唔識游水又唔敢出得太遠，所以可以話係乜都睇唔到....聽同團啲人講要游到好出先睇到，如果係為咗浮建議直接報啲出外海嘅團好啲</blockquote><br />\n翡翠島唔係姐係出海團咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我join嗰個團無帶我哋出海中心度潛水...<br />\n淨係送咗我哋去翡翠島，係海灘間舖仔租器材係個島附近自己游出去玩浮潛</blockquote><br />\n師兄記唔記得你join邊間同幾錢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我嗰陣係市中心啲travel agent舖仔度報咗三個團<br />\n<br />\n翡翠島佢幫我報咗呢間，包個lunch同浮潛工具<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ragingthunder.com.au/fitzroy-island-snorkelling/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ragingthunder.com.au%2Ffitzroy-island-snorkelling%2F&d=H5S4o0Ff8XTpADkL962R5o9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=fc49c929\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ragingthunder.com.au/fitzroy-island-snorkelling/</a><br />\n<br />\n大堡礁潛水我自己睇完上網介紹揀咗呢間Silverswift, 浮潛加一次 scuba diving，個團相對其他團會去得比較遠(揸得好撚快勁多人暈船浪)，污柒少所以大堡礁都靚啲<br />\n<br />\n後尾同有個團友傾計，佢話係Cairns join過唔同公司嘅潛水團，覺得呢間最好，因為佢接散客居多，船上識潛水嘅客比較多，所以船員同教練可以放多啲時間係初學者身上，佢話有join過一次其他團，大部分客都係on99中國大媽，所以教練根本理唔到咁多人<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.silverseries.com.au/swift.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.silverseries.com.au%2Fswift.htm&d=H5S4o0Ff8XTpADkL962R5o9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=c5f3b320\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.silverseries.com.au/swift.htm</a><br />\n(有台灣教練同香港船員)<br />\n<br />\n仲join咗個乜鬼火車加熱帶雨林纜車<br />\n我記得三個團加埋大概五百澳紙鬆啲<br />\nsilver swift最貴好似二百幾，佢個網都有價錢睇，睇你想玩幾多次 scuba dive"},{"pid":"d339814994531b7ac08671739c643cfb3b802ded","tid":421142,"uid":83097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T07:36:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請問有無師兄姐去過cairns?<br />\n<br />\n我想搵一至兩日係出海 想問下綠島同翡翠島有乜野唔同？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">熱帶雨林公園同天空之城</span>係咪值得去？<br />\n<br />\n我地係四個人去 有一個唔識游水 會唔會悶親佢？</blockquote><br />\ngreen for tourist <br />\nfitzroy also for tourist but more local<br />\nred = worth going<br />\nalso go to port douglas and kuranda <br />\nnight time if u like crazy parties and wanna hook up with some hot european chicks then go to a club named gilligans"},{"pid":"f8e7935cac4c830bfcbfe77d137878c2f34fd253","tid":421142,"uid":128271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T03:29:05.000Z","msg":"澳洲跳傘出左事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下星期出發喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}